s here are not verified to the same degree.\n179: dc-creator: Uberon editors\n180: dc-contributor: OBOL\n181: \n182: [sctid-cl]\n183: file: cl-bridge-to-sctid.owl\n184: dc-title: CL bridge to SNOMED-CT\n185: dc-description: Rough subclass axioms between SNOMED-CT and CL. Note that SNOMED is not open, unlike other ontologies used in bridges here. Consequently, the mappings here are not verified to the same degree.\n186: dc-creator: CL editors\n187: dc-contributor: OBOL\n188: \n189: [spd-uberon]\n190: file: uberon-bridge-to-spd.owl\n191: \n192: [spd-cl]\n193: file: cl-bridge-to-spd.owl\n194: \n195: [tads-uberon]\n196: file: uberon-bridge-to-tads.owl\n197: \n198: [tads-cl]\n199: file: cl-bridge-to-tads.owl\n200: \n201: [tgma-uberon]\n202: file: uberon-bridge-to-tgma.owl\n203: add-axiom: (UBERON:0001062 and (BFO:0000050 some NCBITaxon:44484)) SubClassOf: RO:0002160 some NCBITaxon:44484\n204: \n205: [tgma-cl]\n206: file: cl-bridge-to-tgma.owl\n207: \n208: [wbbt-uberon]\n209: file: uberon-bridge-to-wbbt.owl\n210: add-axiom: (UBERON:0001062 and (BFO:0000050 some NCBITaxon:6237)) SubClassOf: RO:0002160 some NCBITaxon:6237\n211: \n212: [wbbt-cl]\n213: file: cl-bridge-to-wbbt.owl\n214: \n215: [wbls-uberon]\n216: file: uberon-bridge-to-wbls.owl\n217: \n218: [xao-uberon]\n219: file: uberon-bridge-to-xao.owl\n220: dc-title: Uberon bridge to xao\n221: dc-description: Taxonomic equivalence axioms between XAO and Uberon.\n222: dc-creator: Uberon editors\n223: dc-contributor: Erik Segerdell\n224: dc-contributor: VG Ponferrada\n225: add-axiom: (UBERON:0001062 and (BFO:0000050 some NCBITaxon:8353)) SubClassOf: RO:0002160 some NCBITaxon:8353\n226: \n227: [xao-cl]\n228: file: cl-bridge-to-xao.owl\n229: dc-title: CL bridge to xao\n230: dc-description: Taxonomic equivalence axioms between XAO and CL.\n231: dc-creator: CL editors\n232: dc-contributor: Erik Segerdell\n233: dc-contributor: VG Ponferrada\n234: \n235: [zfa-uberon]\n236: file: uberon-bridge-to-zfa.owl\n237: dc-title: Uberon bri