{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778904279442,"sessionID":"ses_1d1105b2dffeoypsZAOjVXoVJo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:98","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"Issue #3409 has been addressed in PR #<NN>.\n\nBased on the discussion in the issue thread, the consensus was to use **'in taxon'** (RO:0002162) for taxon-specific bridging axioms involving life stage terms, rather than 'occurs in' (BFO:0000066). The changes implement this across the bridge generation rules and all affected bridge files.\n\nPlease review the PR for full details.\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778904279437,"end":1778904279441}},"id":"prt_e2ef5204900157R6tS8DNsBGH2","sessionID":"ses_1d1105b2dffeoypsZAOjVXoVJo","messageID":"msg_e2ef50fb2001LnZKUQHbw8MU7R"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778904324063,"sessionID":"ses_1d1105b2dffeoypsZAOjVXoVJo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:99","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"## Summary\n\nThis PR addresses issue #3409 by standardizing the relation used in Uberon-generated bridging axioms for life stage terms. Following the discussion in the issue thread, we now use **'in taxon' (RO:0002162)** instead of **'occurs in' (BFO:0000066)** for all life stage bridging axioms.\n\n## Rationale\n\nPreviously, Uberon-generated bridges for externally maintained taxon-specific life stage ontologies (FBdv, WBls, HsapDv, MmusDv, SSLSO, etc.) used `occurs in` (BFO:0000066) in their equivalent class expressions, while the developmental-stage-ontologies repository used `part of` (BFO:0000050). As noted in the issue, this inconsistency across species was problematic. The discussion thread concluded with a consensus (notably from @cmungall and others) that `in taxon` (RO:0002162) is the appropriate relation for attaching life cycle/cycle stage terms to their taxa.\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### 1. Bridge generation rules\n- **`src/ontology/bridge/bridges.rules`**: Changed `TAXREL` for life cycle (`UBERON:0000104`) and life cycle stage (`UBERON:0000105`) terms from `BFO:0000066` to `RO:0002162`.\n- **`src/ontology/bridge/bridge-xao-ls.rules`**: Updated the XAO life stage-specific bridge ruleset to use `RO:0002162` instead of `BFO:0000066`.\n\n### 2. Composite metazoan configuration\n- **`src/ontology/config/taxa.yaml`**: Replaced `BFO:0000066` with `RO:0002162` in the default `unfold_over` compositing setting.\n- **`src/scripts/taxa.py`**: Updated the default `unfold_over` value and corresponding comment to use `RO:0002162`.\n\n### 3. Legacy bridge scripts\n- **`src/ontology/make-bridge-ontologies-from-xrefs.pl`** and **`src/scripts/make-bridge-ontologies-from-xrefs.pl`**: Updated the legacy Perl script to use `in_taxon` / `RO:0002162` instead of `occurs_in` / `BFO:0000066` for life stage cross-references.\n\n### 4. Regenerated bridge OWL files\nThe following bridge files were updated to replace all occurrences of `BFO_0000066` with `RO_0002162` and to declare the new property:\n- `uberon-bridge-to-fbdv.owl`\n- `uberon-bridge-to-fma.owl`\n- `uberon-bridge-to-hsapdv.owl`\n- `uberon-bridge-to-mmusdv.owl`\n- `uberon-bridge-to-sslso.owl`\n- `uberon-bridge-to-wbls.owl`\n- `uberon-bridge-to-xao.owl`\n- `uberon-bridge-to-zfs.owl`\n\n## Checklist\n- [x] Identified all locations where `occurs in` was used for life stage bridges\n- [x] Updated `bridges.rules` (main SSSOM-based bridge generator)\n- [x] Updated `bridge-xao-ls.rules` (XAO life stage bridge)\n- [x] Updated `config/taxa.yaml` and `scripts/taxa.py` (composite compositing defaults)\n- [x] Updated legacy `make-bridge-ontologies-from-xrefs.pl` scripts\n- [x] Regenerated / patched all affected bridge OWL files\n- [x] Verified all modified OWL files parse as well-formed XML\n- [x] Verified no remaining `BFO:0000066` references remain in bridge generation logic\n\nSigned-off-by: @dragon-ai-agent\n","filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778904324056,"end":1778904324062}},"id":"prt_e2ef529f50015xeZtoAQ9l36y6","sessionID":"ses_1d1105b2dffeoypsZAOjVXoVJo","messageID":"msg_e2ef50fb2001LnZKUQHbw8MU7R"}}
