{"type":"text","timestamp":1778904359892,"sessionID":"ses_1d1105b2dffeoypsZAOjVXoVJo","part":{"id":"prt_e2ef61b99001E0nAT0RXDgQPkQ","messageID":"msg_e2ef6075c0014YuNSwf0Wsce7t","sessionID":"ses_1d1105b2dffeoypsZAOjVXoVJo","type":"text","text":"The changes for issue #3409 have been made and committed locally. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n### Changes\n- **`src/ontology/bridge/bridges.rules`**: Updated the bridge generation rules to use `RO:0002162` (`in taxon`) instead of `BFO:0000066` (`occurs in`) for life stage terms (`UBERON:0000104` and `UBERON:0000105`).\n- **`src/ontology/bridge/bridge-xao-ls.rules`**: Updated the XAO life stage bridge rules to use `RO:0002162`.\n- **`src/ontology/config/taxa.yaml`** and **`src/scripts/taxa.py`**: Updated the composite compositing defaults to unfold over `RO:0002162` instead of `BFO:0000066`.\n- **`make-bridge-ontologies-from-xrefs.pl`** (both copies): Updated the legacy bridge script.\n- **Regenerated bridge OWL files**: Updated all life-stage bridge files to use `RO_0002162`, including `uberon-bridge-to-fbdv.owl`, `fma.owl`, `hsapdv.owl`, `mmusdv.owl`, `sslso.owl`, `wbls.owl`, `xao.owl`, and `zfs.owl`.\n\n### Verification\n- All modified OWL bridge files were checked for well-formed XML.\n- No remaining references to `BFO:0000066` exist in the bridge generation logic.\n\n`ISSUE_COMMENTS.md` and `PR_COMMENTS.md` have been created at the repo root.","time":{"start":1778904341401,"end":1778904359889}}}
